{"id": 2926, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得现如今哪些东西可以算当代人的“新型宠物”？", "description": "猫猫狗狗是没空养了，养一只扫地机器人还是没问题的。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Printstock）", "record_count": 7880, "comment_count": 21, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190429174228LJSNc2xaXIiUbvwP.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-29T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5764, "title": "你觉得现如今哪些东西可以算当代人的“新型宠物”？", "content": "你觉得现如今哪些东西可以算当代人的“新型宠物”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 341653, "content": "电脑，出了啥故障会对着它碎碎念好久", "image": "img/option/option/20190429182058cSQmAz3Cp6eiahgY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341654, "content": "手机，总觉得它好像装了一部分自己的灵魂", "image": "img/option/option/20190429182500u7eE3BPWXlbODIrQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341656, "content": "扫地机器人/小家器，打扫得很干净还会表扬它", "image": "img/option/option/20190429182645yNLkYAf9FW38xJCs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341657, "content": "Siri/Cortana/小爱同学，有事没事都会去调戏它一下", "image": "img/option/option/201904291824016IQZ2KDXLRSBwNMm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341658, "content": "手办/乐高，会给它起一些好玩的昵称", "image": "img/option/option/20190429182700m186OBJQgYRKFwCd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341659, "content": "绿植，每次浇水的时候都要对它说“快快长大”", "image": "img/option/option/20190429182328R4CQubn1awfH9GZA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341661, "content": "云养蛙/养兔之类（主角通常是动物）的养成游戏", "image": "img/option/option/20190429182320aQdM6rlJPIuAE59o.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341662, "content": "在社交媒体上长期关注的“云养”萌宠账号", "image": "img/option/option/20190429182234ctQKZT7q4HoS5x1X.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 341652, "content": "车，出发之前还会拍拍它给它加油打气", "image": "img/option/option/201904291820496Zquc4Yfzo9lJ35p.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}